org.hps.monitoring.application.model

Class AbstractModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.monitoring.application.model.AbstractModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConfigurationModel, ConnectionStatusModel, RunModel

    public abstract class AbstractModel
extends Object
    An abstract class which updates a set of listeners when there are property changes to a backing model.
